输出”导航<br>从应用的角度—&gt;“即用即学“。就是落实”输出“的过程，通过“输入”得到的目标来进行“输出“，检索式学习，和要学习的内容打交道，这里希望你能成为一名”抬杠“的人，肯花时间和知识点耗上，想方设法让自己记忆知识点的理解更深刻。要注意：不要耗太久拖延时间，不行就认了去看答案。也不要过于钻牛角尖，因为违背了”输入“给定的目标，不必要的内容不要学，将功夫花在刀刃上。以上是”输出“的要点。<br>3、最后总结，”即学即用“和”即用即学“相辅相成，”输入“：看试卷习体，得到考点后再看书；”输出“：针对考点用”检索式学习“来加深自己对知识点或是题型的印象。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":303255,"user_name":"赌神很低调","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1168545,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1066778E1EDF26","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/d4/a1/8bc8e7e1.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1626688007,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1626688007","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"一句话概括:主动输出，测试所学","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":301980,"user_name":"信仰年轻","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1329011,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B2BD881D25FCDD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/47/73/63a3cb41.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1626008079,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1626008079","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"03｜掌握考试思维：成为一个特别会考试的人<br>1、用考试的思维去学习","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":301760,"user_name":"Better me","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1261959,"ip_address":"","ucode":"CADF08D357489A","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/41/87/46d7e1c2.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625846731,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1625846731","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"思维转换<br>事前分析<br>建立链接","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":301540,"user_name":"子小策","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2660220,"ip_address":"","ucode":"9F16C6AD530AF5","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/28/97/7c/4208a0c1.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625732268,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1625732268","product_id":100081501,"comm